headline: Navient (NAVI) Up 5.6% Since Last Earnings Report: Can It Continue?
summary: Navient (NAVI) reported earnings 30 days ago. What's next for the stock? We take a look at earnings estimates for some clues.

headline: Is your AI bet too big? How to balance with other growth themes
summary: Investors heavily exposed to artificial intelligence (AI) may want to think about where else to put their money as markets shift. Drew Pettit, Citi US equity strategist, explains how fintech and wearable tech could balance out investor portfolios.
